---
layout: layouts/base.njk
templateClass: tmpl-home
---

<main class="home">
  <div class="intro-home">
    <h2>Hello!</h2>
    <p>Welcome to my site! I am a web designer &amp; developer from South Portland, Maine and I love creating things on the web. Please feel free to have a look around and if you are so inclined, I am for hire!</p>
  </div>

  <article class="about-intro">
    <div class="home-container">
      <div class="home-img"><img src="/img/headshot.png" alt="Todd"></div>
        <h3>I've been working in some capacity on the web since 1999. I have been working with computers since 1985. I started programming in BASIC on a Commodore 64 and loved it. I have been programming in some capacity since then, whether personal or professional. I love what I do and I love learning new technologies, sharing my experiences, attending web conferences, and meeting new folks in the industry.</h3>
    </div>
  </article>

  <div class="articles">
    <h3>Latest Articles</h3>
      <ul class="article-sections">
        <li class="article-wrapper">
          {%- for post in collections.userdefendersbookclub | reverse -%}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}"><img src="/img/udbc.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" data-src="/img/udbc.jpg" class="lazyload" />
            <h4>
              {{ post.data.title }}
          {%- endfor -%}
            </h4></a>
        </li>

        <li class="article-wrapper">
          {%- for post in collections.colorcontrast | reverse -%}
          <a href="{{ post.url }}"><img src="/img/fieldnotes.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" data-src="/img/fieldnotes.jpg" class="lazyload" />
            <h4>
              {{ post.data.title }}
          {%- endfor -%}
            </h4></a>
        </li>

        <li class="article-wrapper">
          {%- for post in collections.userdefenderspodcast | reverse -%}
          <a href="{{ post.url }}"><img src="/img/udp.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" data-src="/img/udp.jpg" class="lazyload" />
            <h4>
              {{ post.data.title }}
          {%- endfor -%}
            </h4></a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="copyright">
      <h3>&copy;1999 &mdash;
        <script type="text/javascript">
          var d = new Date();
          document.write(d.getFullYear());
        </script>
        Todd Libby
      </h3>
    </div>
  </main>